description: Saturday's Waffle is a mobile eatery serving up gourmet liege waffles in Salt Lake City. Their menu offers exquisite combinations of fruits, handmade sauces and savory options which provide a truly unique and delicious experience. Specials change with frequency. Come see what all the fuss is about and meet the guys in bow ties as they serve up a delicious start to your weekend.
name: Saturday's Waffle
